9
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:20,800
Wow!

10
00:02:21,200 --> 00:02:23,480
He has such a nice figure.

11
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:24,760
Enough!

12
00:02:26,040 --> 00:02:28,240
Who? Who is looking at you?

13
00:02:28,480 --> 00:02:29,400
Hold on.

14
00:02:30,480 --> 00:02:31,840
Be my guard, please.

15
00:02:34,200 --> 00:02:35,480
