16
00:02:35,600 --> 00:02:36,960
Last time was in the forest.

17
00:02:37,040 --> 00:02:38,480
You're perfect to be my guard.

18
00:02:38,760 --> 00:02:40,120
I've checked your background.

19
00:02:40,240 --> 00:02:41,120
He's very clean now.

20
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:52,600
I'm here to hunt Bai Yuyu.

21
00:02:52,880 --> 00:02:54,320
It's easy to save you.

22
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:55,320
In addition,

23
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:56,760
you haven't done me any good.

24
00:02:56,880 --> 00:02:58,320
Why should I be your guard?

25
00:02:58,880 --> 00:03:01,240
I can help you find Bai Yuyu.

26
00:03:01,760 --> 00:03:03,680
He has a good reputation.

27
00:03:03,880 --> 00:03:06,680
And I'm too poor recently.

28
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:09,240
Alright. Deal is done.

29
00:03:09,320 --> 00:03:10,960
