35
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,600
Protect the prince.

36
00:03:20,480 --> 00:03:21,240
I'm screwed.

37
00:03:21,320 --> 00:03:23,760
We won't be clear if they see this.

38
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:27,480
Second Prince,

39
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:28,480
your Highness.

40
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:29,880
Your Highness.

41
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:31,880
Steward Wang is so flustered.

42
00:03:32,040 --> 00:03:33,960
It must disturb my mood.

43
00:03:35,320 --> 00:03:36,400
And disturb the prince.

44
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:37,760
Please forgive me.

45
00:03:37,880 --> 00:03:39,680
Because the assassin was found in your mansion,

46
00:03:39,760 --> 00:03:41,040
I am worried about your safety.

47
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:42,960
Your Highness, it's good that you're fine.

48
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:45,320
You scared me to death.

49
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,200
Leave now.

50
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:48,320
Understood.

51
00:04:03,040 --> 00:04:05,600
