59
00:04:18,640 --> 00:04:19,360
Oh, right.

60
00:04:19,640 --> 00:04:21,080
What are your requirements?

61
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:23,760
Thirty taels of silver per month.

62
00:04:23,960 --> 00:04:25,000
I guarantee food and lodging.

63
00:04:25,200 --> 00:04:26,080
That's good.

64
00:04:27,080 --> 00:04:27,960
Really?

65
00:04:29,640 --> 00:04:30,640
It's a deal

66
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:35,320
It's a deal

67
00:04:47,520 --> 00:04:48,520
