75
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:00,520
For now.

76
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:02,400
Stand up.

77
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:04,080
Thank you, Third Prince.

78
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:07,800
He was the eldest son,

79
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:10,480
but his mother is sinful,

80
