pose no threat to me.

81
00:05:14,080 --> 00:05:15,680
Second brother has the biggest hope.

82
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:18,480
With the support of Great General Gong Sunzan,

83
00:05:19,080 --> 00:05:20,800
It was unexpected that

84
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:24,120
