95
00:05:56,080 --> 00:05:56,960
Grand Preceptor.

96
00:05:57,640 --> 00:05:59,200
I'm tired today.

97
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:01,600
So much for this game.

98
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:16,120
Your Highness,

99
00:06:16,520 --> 00:06:18,200
I want to see

100
